    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Use spoilers to hide some content on the page using shortcode. On the settings page, you can specify the color of the spoiler.</p>\n<h3>How to use</h3>\n<p>Example: <code>[spoiler]Spoiler content[/spoiler]</code></p>\n<p>Example: <code>[spoiler title=\"Show spoiler\"]Spoiler content[/spoiler]</code></p>\n<h3>Translations</h3>\n<p>You can translate Simple Spoiler on <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/simple-spoiler\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"><strong>translate.wordpress.org</strong></a>.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload folder <code>simple-spoiler</code> to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory;</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress;</li>\n<li>Place shortcode in your content.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='how%20do%20i%20can%20customize%20design%20of%20the%20spoiler%3F'>\nHow do I can customize design of the spoiler?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>To change color layout of a spoiler, please, go to options page.</p>\n</p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed Unauthenticated Arbitrary Shortcode Execution vulnerability in comments.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed Cross Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added support spoiler shortcode for comments.</li>\n<li>Added settings for change spoiler border color.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix undefined constant &#8216;title&#8217;.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
